title: Gorilla Filler Plasterboard & Drywall Mesh Tape 50m
features: Gorilla Filler plasterboard and drywall mesh 50mm x 50cm.

Also knows as jointing tape, this plasterboard and drywall tape used to reinforce internal corner joints between plasterboard, as well as flat joints. Mesh drywall tape has a tacky backing, allowing it to stick to the wall on its own.

A strong white mesh which is easy to apply, measuring 50mm x 50M making sure you have enough mesh to do the job. Mesh tape is more mould resistant than paper tape, this being a great option for use in bathrooms, kitchens, and any other internal locations that may be exposed to water.
The mesh can be used by home DIY enthusiasts or professional traders , giving you a fast and easy solution to repair cracks and patched and crate a perfect joint every time.
